parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power sliding door can cause injuries or even death, especially to children, as the door may shut on them or open unexpectedly while the vehicle is in motion.

gets stuck
and does not respond to the automatic door and window control.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Tank and Filler Tube Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel tank and filler tube can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, accidents, or other safety hazards.
symptoms: Fuel odor inside and outside the vehicle
fuel spraying from the filler neck valve
fuel leaking from the area where the filler tube connects to the fuel tank
fuel pouring from the gas connection pipe that goes into the tank.

lack of amber side reflectors on headlamps.
